name: Contract with the Devil: II
description:
The deed is done. I have my soul back.
I looked across the table at him 
as I felt the weight of my spirit 
settle in my chest, 
a foreign thing, a body of water, 
a stone, a pendulum. 
I saw his eyes and I knew 
that he didn't know the feeling, 
he didn't know and he didn't care.
